WEBVTT

00:00.023 --> 00:01.523
Previously on "Midnight, Texas"...

00:01.526 --> 00:03.629
- Joe is an angel.
- Fallen angel.

00:03.632 --> 00:04.828
Did not suspect that.

00:04.830 --> 00:06.535
I found this. Someone
could have seen you.

00:06.536 --> 00:08.304
The veil that Midnight sits upon,

00:08.307 --> 00:10.534
it's fraying, and evil
is being drawn here.

00:10.535 --> 00:12.234
He's a killer. That's who he is.

00:12.235 --> 00:15.200
He was my son.

00:15.201 --> 00:16.700
I used my light to save her,

00:16.701 --> 00:18.534
which means they will be coming for me.

00:18.535 --> 00:20.234
You chose to protect

00:20.235 --> 00:21.934
all the evil things that he did.

00:21.935 --> 00:23.400
You're all I have left.

00:23.401 --> 00:25.400
I don't ever want to see you again.

00:25.401 --> 00:28.400
Chuy, it's not safe for
you in Midnight anymore.

00:28.401 --> 00:29.868
Stay away.

00:32.735 --> 00:36.567
_

00:36.568 --> 00:40.567
So, how'd it feel?

00:40.568 --> 00:44.267
I don't know. How should it feel?

00:44.268 --> 00:47.300
Oh, for me, there's nothing better.

00:47.301 --> 00:49.234
Definitely didn't feel like that.

00:49.235 --> 00:52.600
I've been fighting demon for millennia.

00:52.601 --> 00:54.734
First time's hard,

00:54.735 --> 00:57.600
but you do it enough, you gain skills,

00:57.601 --> 01:00.567
confidence,

01:00.568 --> 01:02.500
and then it gets fun.

01:05.001 --> 01:07.467
This group, out of
the veil, they were...

01:07.468 --> 01:10.634
they were rough, and
you handled them bravely.

01:10.635 --> 01:12.600
Appreciate you saying so.

01:12.601 --> 01:15.634
Our first battle together.

01:15.635 --> 01:17.173
It won't be our last.

01:23.635 --> 01:26.300
I taught him everything I knew,

01:26.301 --> 01:28.700
and he left.

01:28.701 --> 01:31.434
He just up and left.

01:31.435 --> 01:33.767
But he popped up on my radar recently.

01:33.768 --> 01:37.367
I think he's here.

01:37.368 --> 01:41.467
So, what are you doing in these parts?

01:41.468 --> 01:43.467
The pull.

01:43.468 --> 01:46.500
I was laying low in
Shreveport when I felt it...

01:46.501 --> 01:49.534
this powerful pull

01:49.535 --> 01:53.734
telling me to get my ass to Midnight.

01:53.735 --> 01:57.394
Well, I'm afraid
you're not gonna make it.

01:59.635 --> 02:01.601
I'm not?

02:04.468 --> 02:06.467
Nope.

02:06.468 --> 02:09.667
Because you're a demon.

02:09.668 --> 02:12.667
You're the scourge of the universe.

02:14.435 --> 02:18.367
I do believe that if
you're all exterminated,

02:18.368 --> 02:20.500
this world would be a better place.

02:20.501 --> 02:23.226
Who the hell do you...

02:25.000 --> 02:31.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

02:38.835 --> 02:40.635
An angel?

02:46.435 --> 02:48.368
Give the man a prize.

02:54.173 --> 02:59.212
- <font color="#D81D1D">Synced and corrected by VitoSilans</font> -
